overview: A single woman will meet 14 men who have everything to please her. She is unaware that, as in everyday life, some men she is going to meet are not there for sincere reasons... They are seducers! And if one of them succeeds in being the chosen one of his heart, he will win 20,000 euros. Will our single person succeed in detecting true love and avoiding the trap of seducers?
